[There are 10 states in the nation of South Sudan, as can be seen on this map: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/States_of_South_Sudan.

Up to this point, many of the cases have been in the eastern part of the country, both in the south (Eastern Equatoria State) and north (Upper Nile State) but with a few cases in the central eastern state, Jonglei. - Mod.LL

